acked by Somalian Pirates in 2011.","genre_ids":[28,10752,18,36,12,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5048,"vote_count":79,"poster_path":"/oAI8whpvqWxxucVGJdDiGOfCjMB.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-27","vote_average":7.709,"backdrop_path":"/bedJLAIR7dxP423YMIpTXhrFCvH.jpg","original_title":"PASKAL: The Movie","original_language":"ms"},{"id":25647,"adult":false,"title":"Breath","video":false,"overview":"A condemned prisoner slowly falls in love with the married female artist who decorates his prison cell. Jin is a convicted killer awaiting execution on Death Row; Yeon is a lonely artist locked in a loveless marriage.","genre_ids":[80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6848,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/tXAw0cdVidJpiWdW1ArMCU8T2cq.jpg","release_date":"2007-04-26","vote_average":6.683,"backdrop_path":"/3Wr9M9Pee1kLgfbRSrG0LHy0GsP.jpg","original_title":"숨","original_language":"ko"},{"id":483435,"adult":false,"title":"All About Nina","video":false,"overview":"Nina Geld's passion and talent have made her a rising star in the comedy scene, but she's an emotional mess offstage. When a new professional opportunity coincides with a romantic one, she is forced to confront her own deeply troubled past.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6849,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/qcOV7ALpm0CiIyeTxP3Ncjrc7HA.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-28","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/qvlToqIqsAY0qcFtGXXK1v2xDFl.jpg","original_title":"All About Nina","original_language":"en"},{"id":122126,"adult":false,"title":"The Concubine","video":false,"overview":"Living a torturous life of poverty and barely able to survive, Hwa-yeon decides to offer herself as one of the king’s concubines. Once inside the royal palace, two men are immediately seized by the woman - the Grand Prince Seong-won, a megalomaniacal ruler drunk with power and lust, and Kwon-yoo, who has everything to lose if his desire for Hwa-yeon is exposed.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5