9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"A Taxi Driver | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"May, 1980. Man-seob is a taxi driver in Seoul who lives from hand to mouth, raising his young daughter alone. One day, he hears that there is a foreigner who will pay big money for a drive down to Gwangju city. Not knowing that he’s a German journalist with a hidden agenda, Man-seob takes the job."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/131111/a-taxi-driver"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"A Taxi Driver"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"May, 1980. Man-seob is a taxi driver in Seoul who lives from hand to mouth, raising his young daughter alone. One day, he hears that there is a foreigner who will pay big money for a drive down to Gwangju city. Not knowing that he’s a German journalist with a hidden agenda, Man-seob takes the job."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/131111/a-taxi-driver"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iXVaWbxmyPk4KZGZk5GGDGFieMX.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"A Taxi Driver"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"May, 1980. Man-seob is a taxi driver in Seoul who lives from hand to mouth, raising his young daughter alone. One day, he hears that there is a foreigner who will pay big money for a drive down to Gwangju city. Not knowing that he’s a German journalist with a hidden agenda, Man-seob takes the job."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://imag